br />\n<br />\n唔好搵唔發達做黎做乜鳩？<br />\n做工程你估輕鬆？<br />\n由上至下 個個日日屌黎屌去賴黎賴去 鬥卸膊<br />\n環境又差 又危險<br />\n唔發達 又冇前景<br />\n做黎做乜鳩？"},{"pid":"953ead6a9518e6b40466a9c771c88a5c626b1d16","tid":2318042,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"淨係做維修  政府外判野都餓唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓只會愈來愈多<br />\n<br />\n加埋教育局幫手 冇人讀數冇工業學院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點會有供應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae352ae390c92d7921f923a63f3f0765d3d5192","tid":2318042,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"028960a574e88739e9ac0ba542227fedbf602ae6","tid":2318042,"uid":83102,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"你第一句<br />\n先唔講好唔好 發唔發達<br />\n<br />\n唔好搵唔發達做黎做乜鳩？<br />\n做工程你估輕鬆？<br />\n由上至下 個個日日屌黎屌去賴黎賴去 鬥卸膊<br />\n環境又差 又危險<br />\n唔發達 又冇前景<br />\n做黎做乜鳩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"入職2皮好過好多豆系你唔講？"},{"pid":"c685c9d0c47b43ef546821592b26bf0776664037","tid":2318042,"uid":225192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"六天工作為番工而番工<br />\n俾狗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81974994d8df81c5e9fc501023dd58a6be8b0997","tid":2318042,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"倒垃圾晚晚有工開全年無休"},{"pid":"05bd474e4edab9b6d09b0e068aaedba6c318a479","tid":2318042,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"81974994d8df81c5e9fc501023dd58a6be8b0997","tid":2318042,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"倒垃圾晚晚有工開全年無休"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:35:41.000Z","msg":"倒垃圾係工既一種<br />\n<br />\n地盤入面好多種 qs bs pc 騙頭 師傅 管工 老總 工程師 安全 環保 打理 則師 等"},{"pid":"e3e3f39073160e249b8ffe8abeead7f4daaaf589","tid":2318042,"uid":763